OL,3,CThe Treasury audit: Political theatre
OL,4,Cor shocking revelation?
OL,6,FReeves will say that an assessment by
OL,7,FTreasury officials has unearthed a gap
OL,8,Fin department spending plans that runs
OL,9,Finto "tens of billions of pounds" for
OL,10,Fthis year alone - a funding gap she'll
OL,11,Faccuse the previous government of
OL,12,Fconcealing in its desperation to cut
OL,13,Ftaxes in the run up to the election.
OL,15,FThe chancellor will say this is an
OL,16,Foverspend that no one knew about and
OL,17,Fone that runs across many government
OL,18,Fdepartments.
