OL,3,CThe Treasury audit: Political theatre
OL,4,Cor shocking revelation?
OL,6,F"Upon my arrival at the Treasury three
OL,7,Fweeks ago, it became clear that there
OL,8,Fwere things I didn't know. Things the
OL,9,Fparty opposite covered up from the
OL,10,Fcountry," Reeves will tell parliament.
OL,12,F"It's time to level with the public
OL,13,Fand tell them the truth."
OL,15,FThe Treasury audit is set to reveal
OL,16,Fmore about the pressures on government
OL,17,Fspending and public services than we
OL,18,Fknew previously.
