OL,3,CThe Treasury audit: Political theatre
OL,4,Cor shocking revelation?
OL,6,FThe IFS has been warning for months
OL,7,Fthat the existing spending plans
OL,8,Fbeyond next March look implausible - a
OL,9,Fview that was shared by the National
OL,10,FInstitute for Economic and Social
OL,11,FResearch, The International Monetary
OL,12,FFund and The Organisation for Economic
OL,13,FCooperation and Development.
OL,15,FDuring the election campaign, the IFS
OL,16,Faccused Labour and the other major
OL,17,Fparties of failing to engage with the
OL,18,Frisk there would need to be
OL,19,Fsignificant cuts or tax rises that
OL,20,Fweren't in the manifestos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
