OL,3,CThe Treasury audit: Political theatre
OL,4,Cor shocking revelation?
OL,6,F"I think there's a degree of political
OL,7,Ftheatre (to the audit) and a degree of
OL,8,F'some of this really is worse than
OL,9,Fexpected,'" said Paul Johnson,
OL,10,FDirector of the IFS.
OL,12,F"The government is probably getting
OL,13,Fpeople used to the idea that there's
OL,14,Fgoing to be more taxing or more
OL,15,Fborrowing in a Budget that we see in
OL,16,Fthe Autumn."
OL,18,FIFS Director Paul Johnson told ITV
OL,19,FNews he thinks 'there's a degree of
OL,20,Fpolitical theatre' to the chancellor's
OL,21,Faudit
