OL,3,CThe Treasury audit: Political theatre
OL,4,Cor shocking revelation?
OL,6,FThe idea Labour would struggle to
OL,7,Fimplement the spending plans they
OL,8,Finherited is not remotely new - it has
OL,9,Fbeen widely predicted and for some
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FThe recent economic news has been
OL,13,Fencouraging, but the combination of
OL,14,Fhigh debt, higher interest rates and
OL,15,Funheroic economic growth means the
OL,16,Fgovernment's finances are in a
OL,17,Fgenuinely dreadful position and it
OL,18,Freally is a difficult time to be a
OL,19,Fchancellor.
OL,21,FBut it's worth remembering two things.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
